longBusinessSummary: Hacksaw AB (publ) operates as a B2B technology platform and game development company. It develops and distributes games comprising digital slots, scratch cards, and instant win games for private and state-owned iGaming operators, as well as develops remote gaming servers. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
